      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic driving experience with this well-maintained vehicle! It's in great condition overall and has clearly been cared for, offering a smooth and reliable ride for its next owner. While you'll find some standard signs of light use consistent with its age, it remains a sharp-looking and dependable choice for any driver.",
