    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been preserved with the utmost care. The exterior paint is flawless, free of any chips, scratches, or swirl marks, and the interior still carries a new-car feel with pristine upholstery and zero wear on the touchpoints. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a complete service history and every component functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
