    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant restoration or may serve best as a donor car for parts. The exterior shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust patches, faded paint, and several dents. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul and the transmission is slipping, making it currently unreliable for daily driving. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a true project car for someone with the time and resources to bring it back to life.",
