    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it has been such a dream to drive. It's in really wonderful shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years! This is the perfect find for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks sharp and feels great on the road. I've kept up with all the maintenance, so it's totally ready for its next big adventure with you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I just know you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine with its signature 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels through a functional M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains tight, utilizing its original hydraulic steering rack for superior tactile feedback. Significant mechanical maintenance has been addressed, including preventative rod bearing replacement and a recent throttle actuator service. The suspension retains its factory-correct damping characteristics, ensuring the car handles with the neutral balance intended by the M Division. A mechanically sound, driver-oriented machine with a documented service history.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Well-maintained. Reliable performance. Clean title. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained, dependable vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior presents beautifully in its original paint, showing only minor, expected road wear that does not detract from its overall appeal. Inside, you'll find a smoke-free cabin with clean upholstery, crisp instrumentation, and a fully functional climate control system. Mechanically, this car is sound; it has undergone regular fluid changes, and the engine runs smooth and quiet with no leaks or warning lights. It delivers a comfortable, confident ride whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip. Complete with a detailed service history and recent inspection, this is a solid choice for anyone seeking a high-quality pre-owned vehicle without the premium price tag of a showroom model.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
